title: Native Instruments Reakor5 Players - Updated - Uranium Willy
description:
This is an update to my last torrent with the various Reaktor Players (which seems to have gotten credited to anonymous somehow over time).

The torrent includes these players and ensembles for Reaktor 5 (Molekular only will play on 5.9 and I have a torrent for that as well at Piratebay as well. You can search user name uraniumwilly and you should find it and other cracked versions seem to making the rounds suddenly. But you will need it!):

Prism
Mikro Prism
Skanner
Razor
Spark
The Finger
The Mouth
Molekular
Monark
Ultraloop

They are all working on my WIN 7 right now just fine. Up to you to figure out how they work and make music with them. Good luck. 

I live in China and my net can be bad at times, but things will go through. Hopefully some people with better connections will get this and get seeding ASAP as these are really wonderful music tools. 

NOTE: As far as I can figure you will have to drop your own loops into The Finger and Molekular to get them to make sounds. Drop some loops you have and then start mutating them all to hell. 

Enjoy

Uranium Willy
